The evidence with the title 'US wealth inequality - top 0.1% worth as much as the bottom 90 ... ' says Nov 13, 2014  ... The share of wealth owned by the top 0.1 % is almost the same as the bottom 90 %  ... To 23 % in 2012 - just one percentage point above the top 0.1%.  ... The richest 1 % of people ( by income) have increased their income  ... In Australia , for example , the top 1% earned 4.8% of the country's income in 1980. 
